Remic mortgage securities offered by Goldman, Sachs &amp; Co. The
offering, Series 1990-118, is backed by Fannie Mae 8 1/2%
securities.
   Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp. -- $315 million of Remic
mortgage securities offered by Kidder, Peabody &amp; Co. The
offering, Series FHLMC Gold Remic 1004, is backed by Freddie
