</IN>
<LP>
   Brunswick Corp., Skokie, Ill., said it expects to report a
one-time gain of $45 to $50 million from dispositions of
non-defense, Technical businesses in 1990.
   Such a gain would represent about 51 cents a share to 57
cents a share, the maker of marine and recreation products
said.
</LP>
