Technetics divisions.
   Net proceeds from dispositions, which could range from
$120 million to $150 million "depending on which transactions
are closed," will be used to pay down debt, Brunswick said.
   For the first six months, Brunswick had net income of
$34.2 million, or 39 cents a share, on sales of $1.36
billion.
